flowchart TB
    U([User / 用户]) --> I[Task Intake / 任务入口]
    I --> C[Control Center / 总控中心]

    subgraph Governance[Governance Layer / 治理层]
      direction LR
      P[Planning Center / 规划中心]
      R[Review Center / 评审中心]
      D[Dispatch Center / 调度中心]
    end

    C --> P
    P --> R
    R --> D
    R -. Revise / 退回修订 .-> P

    subgraph Execution[Execution Layer / 执行层]
      direction LR
      S1[Code Specialist / 代码专家]
      S2[Data Specialist / 数据专家]
      S3[Docs Specialist / 文档专家]
      S4[Search Specialist / 搜索专家]
      S5[Deploy Specialist / 部署专家]
    end

    D --> S1
    D --> S2
    D --> S3
    D --> S4
    D --> S5

    S1 --> A[Result Archive / 结果归档]
    S2 --> A
    S3 --> A
    S4 --> A
    S5 --> A
    A --> O([Delivery / 最终交付])

    classDef io fill:#0b3b2e,stroke:#34d399,color:#eafff7,stroke-width:1.5px;
    classDef main fill:#0f172a,stroke:#60a5fa,color:#e5eefc,stroke-width:1.5px;
    classDef specialist fill:#3b0764,stroke:#c084fc,color:#faf5ff,stroke-width:1.5px;
    class U,O io;
    class I,C,P,R,D,A main;
    class S1,S2,S3,S4,S5 specialist;
